00:46:21.131 --> 00:46:22.810
So I think that's
built into what we do,

00:46:22.810 --> 00:46:25.665
that there's times
where it ebbs and flows.

00:46:25.665 --> 00:46:27.790
ASHLEY PARK: I like to
trick my body into thinking,

00:46:27.790 --> 00:46:30.040
and this is a problem
of mine, like not

00:46:30.040 --> 00:46:32.240
