sometimes to go about it.

00:46:56.450 --> 00:46:58.390
But it makes it more fun.

00:46:58.390 --> 00:46:59.835
I don't know.

00:46:59.835 --> 00:47:00.960
ARIANA DEBOSE: No, totally.

