I will say, that's been a
really nice through line

00:47:20.050 --> 00:47:23.530
about all the extra that comes
with this amazing opportunity.

00:47:23.530 --> 00:47:25.060
I can rely on my show.

00:47:25.060 --> 00:47:25.920
ASHLEY PARK: Show,
it's a safe place.

00:47:25.920 --> 00:47:28.045
ARIANA DEBOSE: I always
have my show to go back to.

