I permitted for other shows.

00:47:40.490 --> 00:47:42.850
So because "Mean Girls" is
also like a party on stage

00:47:42.850 --> 00:47:43.950
every night.

00:47:43.950 --> 00:47:45.366
CHRIS JACKSON:
Have you also found

00:47:45.366 --> 00:47:47.770
that the more physically
demanding the show

00:47:47.770 --> 00:47:51.410
